cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.CV 

This paper deals with information fusion in the context of multi-sensor target tracking, which is a topic related to systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also analyzes and compares the second-order statistics of different fusion methods, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.AI). The application of weighted Gaussian mixtures also suggests a connection to mathematical analysis (cs.MA) and computer vision (cs.CV).
